OL,3,C'IKEA driver killed our dog then
OL,4,Ccompany offered us #50,' say
OL,5,Cdevastated owners
OL,7,FA family has told Rags Martel how
OL,8,Ftheir Chihuahua was run over and
OL,9,Fkilled by a delivery driver who failed
OL,10,Fto notice what happened
OL,12,FA Potters Bar family has been left
OL,13,Fdistraught after an IKEA delivery
OL,14,Fdriver ran over and killed their dog -
OL,15,Fthen the company offered them #50
OL,16,Fcompensation.
OL,18,FHayley Faulkner was walking her 5-year-
OL,19,Fold Chihuahua Elvis in Rushfield, when
OL,20,Fthe driver pulled out onto the road.
