OL,3,C'IKEA driver killed our dog then
OL,4,Ccompany offered us #50,' say
OL,5,Cdevastated owners
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News London, she said:
OL,8,F"He just pulled out and run my dog
OL,9,Fover while Elvis was on the lead.
OL,11,F"If I hadn't pulled Elvis, he'd have
OL,12,Frun him over on the back wheels as
OL,13,Fwell. I was screaming for him to stop.
OL,14,FHe never stopped."
OL,16,FNeighbours rushed to see what was
OL,17,Fgoing on as Ms Faulkner was left
OL,18,Fscreaming, alongside her one-year-old
OL,19,Fgrandson who had been with them at the
OL,20,Ftime.
