OL,3,C'IKEA driver killed our dog then
OL,4,Ccompany offered us #50,' say
OL,5,Cdevastated owners
OL,7,FIt appeared the driver had not
OL,8,Frealised what had happened.
OL,10,FThe incident was caught on CCTV, but
OL,11,Fit is too graphic to show in full.
OL,13,FIt has left Ms Faulkner traumatised
OL,14,Fand struggling with flashbacks.
OL,16,F"If you love a dog like I love mine,
OL,17,Fthey are my family. I just feel lost
OL,18,Fwithout him," she said.
OL,20,FEven their older dog, Billy is missing
OL,21,FElvis.
