OL,3,C'IKEA driver killed our dog then
OL,4,Ccompany offered us #50,' say
OL,5,Cdevastated owners
OL,7,FHer husband Chris Akhurst contacted
OL,8,FIkea but was left shocked when the
OL,9,Ffurniture company offered them #50 in
OL,10,Fcompensation.
OL,12,FMr Akhurst said: "It's not about the
OL,13,Fmoney. It's just trying to find a
OL,14,Flittle bit of justice and make them
OL,15,Funderstand what they've actually done."
OL,17,F"I think they should have taken
OL,18,Fresponsibility for their actions and
OL,19,Fat least have said sorry," Ms Faulkner
OL,20,Fsaid.
