OL,3,C'IKEA driver killed our dog then
OL,4,Ccompany offered us #50,' say
OL,5,Cdevastated owners
OL,7,FIKEA did increase its compensation to
OL,8,Fthe family first to #300 and then
OL,9,Fupped it to #800 on the day ITV News
OL,10,FLondon ran the story.
OL,12,FBut IKEA is yet to respond to ITV News
OL,13,FLondon's inquiries.
OL,15,FHertfordshire Constabulary is
OL,16,Finvestigating the collision.
